{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":569486,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真正的世界一流大学应有多个专门的部门负责处理校内的非学术问题，不论是误会还是犯罪都应有责任使事情体面地被解决","timestamp":1605687532,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569488,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不论性别，我们面对的是同样的一个社会问题，寻求制度性的解决方式才能防止类似事件再次发生","timestamp":1605687554,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569496,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 理应是这样的，但现在没有人管性骚扰是真的","timestamp":1605687625,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569497,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"支持dz","timestamp":1605687650,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569500,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"党委学生部与法务部共同成立学生社会问题处理办公室","timestamp":1605687678,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569510,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 理应是这样但没有可能是这样，只能挑重点解决，就像国家一样，没有那么多社会资源，这种事儿一年发生十次，一次处理三天，剩下300多天这部门工作人员就睡觉？我不认为这样合理","timestamp":1605687763,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569514,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"寻求制度性解决+1，但这事我说了不算","timestamp":1605687831,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569517,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 我只能说国外一流高校都有这种部门，当然，他们也负责处理hate crime等等其他事务，以及心理辅导","timestamp":1605687850,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569520,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"台湾有，性别平等委员会","timestamp":1605687871,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569535,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你这样说合理，但专门处理性骚扰一件事确实不太合理，的确当有这样一个部门统筹处理一篮子的社会问题，不能细化分类。","timestamp":1605688032,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569541,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 只要有人管就好了","timestamp":1605688111,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":569554,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":118736,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 对","timestamp":1605688185,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":118736,"reply":12,"tag":null,"text":"真正的世界一流大学应有一个专门的部门负责处理校内的性骚扰问题，不论是误会还是犯罪都应有责任使事情体面地被解决","timestamp":1605687461,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782651,"url":"","vote":{}}}